{"tid":1894371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 突發 真。炸彈 ] 一呎長炮彈驚現黃竹坑街頭！ 警方封鎖附近一帶調查","createTime":"2020-02-24T01:04:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T01:06:27.000Z","uid":168161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ae948042831f281e983b8ec7e5fcfa9212b3600f","tid":1894371,"uid":168161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T01:04:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200224/VPGNGR6RGZLDRDR6HH572PBR5E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200224%2FVPGNGR6RGZLDRDR6HH572PBR5E%2F&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpApmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=9d374f7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200224%2FVPGNGR6RGZLDRDR6HH572PBR5E%2F&h=3875df0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200224/VPGNGR6RGZLDRDR6HH572PBR5E/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200224/large/1582505778_99a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200224%2Flarge%2F1582505778_99a5.jpg&h=bd9970c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃竹坑業發街金寶大廈對開，早上7時許，一個約一呎長的炮彈，被放置在大廈對開地面，警方接報封鎖附近一帶範圍，並召來爆炸品處理課到場。<br />\n<br />\n有街坊表示，炮彈原先放在金寶大廈對開的一張凳上，有清潔女工不知就裏，竟將它搬到路邊。<br />\n<br />\n現時港鐵黃竹坑站不准乘客逗留，並封鎖其中一個出入口。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/vYJ7kB3q2cS7Y6_ulM7tZki2Euo=/802x420/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/7DATUJVT4WXNMOMKRAFT7A6GAE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FvYJ7kB3q2cS7Y6_ulM7tZki2Euo%3D%2F802x420%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F7DATUJVT4WXNMOMKRAFT7A6GAE.jpg&h=a533ed56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方封鎖附近範圍。 翁鈺輝攝<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublish